item.description:
I considered a switch to the Congo theme for Hugo. The one thing I didn&rsquo;t like in it was the way it handles inline backticks - it displays them, in addition to formatting the enclosed text as code.
To fix it, create assets/css/custom.css with the following contents:
.prose code::before { content: &#39;&#39; } .prose code::after { content: &#39;&#39; }
